---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Francis Pires — developer and data analyst based in Brazil."
>
  <div class="content-container page-wrap">

    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <span class="bc-d">$</span>
      <span class="bc-c">cat</span>
      <span class="bc-p">./about.md</span>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-block">
      <div class="tb-bar">
        <span class="dot red"></span>
        <span class="dot amber"></span>
        <span class="dot green"></span>
        <span class="tb-file">whoami.sh</span>
      </div>

      <div class="tb-body">
        <div class="cmd"><span class="dollar">$</span> <span class="cmd-text">./whoami.sh</span></div>

        <div class="out">
          <p><span class="k">name</span>: <span class="v">Francis Pires</span></p>
          <p><span class="k">location</span>: <span class="v">Brazil 🇧🇷</span></p>
          <p><span class="k">role</span>: <span class="v">Developer · Data Analyst</span></p>
          <p><span class="k">stack</span>: <span class="v">Python · SQL · JavaScript · dbt · Power BI</span></p>
          <p><span class="k">education</span>: <span class="v">Computer Engineering @ FIAP · Programming @ FIA</span></p>
          <p><span class="k">languages</span>: <span class="v">Português 🇧🇷 · English 🇺🇸</span></p>
          <p><span class="k">interests</span>: <span class="v">data pipelines · open source · music · woodworking</span></p>
          <p>
            <span class="k">github</span>:&nbsp;
            <a href="https://github.com/francispires" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="v link">
              @francispires
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <br />

        <div class="cmd">
          <span class="dollar">$</span>
          <span class="cmd-text">cat ./bio.txt</span>
        </div>

        <div class="out bio lang-en">
          <p>
            I'm a developer and data analyst passionate about turning raw data into
            actionable insights. I spend most of my time building data pipelines,
            writing SQL, and wiring Python together with whatever tools the problem
            calls for.
          </p>
          <p>
            I studied Computer Engineering at FIAP and Programming at FIA.
            Outside of code I enjoy music, woodworking, game development, and
            finding creative uses for math.
          </p>
          <p>
            This site is where I document what I learn — in English, Portuguese,
            or both, depending on the topic and who I think needs to read it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="out bio lang-pt">
          <p>
            Sou desenvolvedor e analista de dados apaixonado por transformar dados brutos em
            insights acionáveis. Passo a maior parte do tempo construindo pipelines de dados,
            escrevendo SQL e conectando Python com as ferramentas que cada problema exige.
          </p>
          <p>
            Estudei Engenharia de Computação na FIAP e Programação na FIA.
            Fora do código, gosto de música, marcenaria, desenvolvimento de games e
            encontrar usos criativos para a matemática.
          </p>
          <p>
            Este site é onde documento o que aprendo — em inglês, português,
            ou nos dois idiomas, dependendo do tema e de quem precisa ler.
          </p>
        </div>

        <br />

        <div class="cmd">
          <span class="dollar">$</span>
          <span class="cursor">_</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-wrap { padding-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 4rem; }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .bc-d { color: var(--green); }
  .bc-c { color: var(--cyan); }
  .bc-p { color: var(--text-dim); }

  .terminal-block {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
  }

  .tb-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .dot {
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .dot.red   { background: var(--red); }
  .dot.amber { background: var(--amber); }
  .dot.green { background: var(--green); }

  .tb-file { margin-left: auto; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); }

  .tb-body { padding: 1.5rem; }

  .cmd {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .dollar   { color: var(--green); }
  .cmd-text { color: var(--cyan); }

  .cursor {
    color: var(--green);
    animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink { 50% { opacity: 0; } }

  .out {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .k    { color: var(--cyan); }
  .v    { color: var(--text); }
  .link { text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .link:hover { color: var(--green); }

  .bio { color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.8; gap: 0.75rem; }
</style>
